Kämik k'ut, are wa' ri qas q'ij ri xuchomaj ri Dios chi kuk'ut na ru Loq' Pixab' chqawäch. Are k'u ri Dios ri To'l Qe, are yo'winaq wa' pa nu q'ab'. In u taqom k'u chutzijoxik we tzij ri'.
