Ri Jesús cäpaki puwi' jun juyub rech cuya tijonicAretak ri Jesús xeril ri q'uialaj winak, xpaki puwi' ri juyub, xt'uyi chila'. Xquimulij c'u quib ru tijoxelab ruc'.
Ri Jesús cuya tijonic chrij ru jachic quib juc'ulaj winak(Cäch'aw chi ri Jesús, cubij:) Xukuje' xbix can nabe: “Apachin ri cujach bi ri rixokil, rajwaxic cuya bi jun wuj che ri cubij wi chi jachom canok,” —cächa'.
